WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:02.500
Voting in the U elections.

00:00:03.160 --> 00:00:04.440
You know the European elections

00:00:04.441 --> 00:00:07.101
are one of the biggest democratic votes in the world.

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:09.080
Every five years,

00:00:09.081 --> 00:00:12.701
voters choose over 700 members of the European Parliament

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:14.340
who represent you.

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:19.060
Once elected, they sit in political groups based on shared beliefs.

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:25.260
Now EU citizens can vote and stand for election in their own country

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:27.540
or the EU country they live in.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:33.640
Your vote decides how Parliament decides on the things that matter.

00:00:33.641 --> 00:00:36.101
The economy, energy and climate.

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:37.980
Europe's place in the world.

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:41.040
By voting, you make your voice heard.

00:00:41.041 --> 00:00:43.501
You help choose the next European Parliament,

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:46.420
and you decide on your future.
